        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Freights First Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill eliminates Amtrak's preference over freight transportation in using a rail line, junction, or crossing if such rail line, junction, or crossing is located within 50 miles of a port or rail yard. Currently, Amtrak's priority status does not apply if there is&amp;nbsp;an emergency.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
